nodes.text: DFS-1308 was one of the Vulture droids in DFS Starfighter Squadron, assigned to Saak'ak during the Blockade of Naboo. It analyzed but was unable to calculate the "Human element" inside the N-1 starfighter.
The image used to represent DFS-1308 is a frame captured from The Phantom Menace which was slightly modified by artists at Decipher, Inc. The same frame was also used to represent DFS-1104.
